column1: No delays due to collisions this morning

column3: Regular traffic reports will resume Friday March 27 at 7:00 a.m.

column4: Please be patient at signalized intersections.
Signals are timed for much higher traffic volumes than our streets are currently experiencing.
Waits on side streets may seem long, but once the main streets are accessed, travel should be faster with much less delays than under normal conditions.
